        will take appropriate steps to delete it promptly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes
        in our practices, technology, or legal requirements. Any updates will be
        posted within the app or on our website, and the effective date will be
        revised accordingly. We encourage you to review this policy
        periodically.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy
        Policy or your personal data, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        Phone: +234 70000000000<br />
